WEBVTT

00:05:59.625 --> 00:06:04.434
has been among the most
significant humane changes

00:06:04.458 --> 00:06:07.333
in US immigration policy ever.

00:06:08.250 --> 00:06:10.601
And that humane change

00:06:10.625 --> 00:06:13.792
imposed order on chaos.

00:06:15.625 --> 00:06:19.434
So where does this leave
Central Americans,

00:06:19.458 --> 00:06:20.833
like Juan Carlos?

00:06:22.333 --> 00:06:24.601
Well, Central Americans received

00:06:24.625 --> 00:06:30.851
just three percent of the guest worker
visas issued in 2019,